node.text: It was truly an honor to speak at @freedomhouse in Charlotte today… The message that I felt I was to deliver was overwhelmingly received. People all around America need to hear a message of unity and hope. I delivered that message today. And a bit more… Thank you @troymaxwell and @pennymaxwell for the invitation, your church is a place filled with joy, peace and freedom.
